WEBVTT

00:00:05.708 --> 00:00:10.875
Every 7 years the cells in the human
body undergo a transformation.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:14.833
The older cells disintegrate
and do not retain their identity.

00:00:14.958 --> 00:00:18.332
But those among them responsible for
the functions of the human body...

00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:21.708
i.e. those which are intangible
but exist in the greater universe...

00:00:21.750 --> 00:00:24.750
constitute the life force
of the human body.

00:00:24.875 --> 00:00:28.000
Sometimes cancerous cells
may be found in the human body.

00:00:28.375 --> 00:00:30.535
But those cells are anomalous
and independent entities.

00:00:30.583 --> 00:00:33.416
These cells have a negative
effect on the life force.

00:00:33.541 --> 00:00:36.166
And are repugnant to the body.

00:00:36.208 --> 00:00:38.375
For the body, this could be...

