I have seen many like you

00:08:29.541 --> 00:08:33.291
I won't allow that poison
in this house anymore

00:08:33.458 --> 00:08:37.290
Oh really? I'll take it again.
Let me see how you stop me

00:08:37.291 --> 00:08:41.749
You know Mr. Byomkesh I have kept
his house under strict surveillance

00:08:41.750 --> 00:08:43.582
