Has Bidhubabu arrived?

00:09:32.333 --> 00:09:33.958
Thank you, I am coming right now!

00:09:34.041 --> 00:09:35.666
Ajit, pass me the cigarette packet

00:09:36.916 --> 00:09:38.540
Byomkesh babu, I mean..
Yes, say

00:09:38.541 --> 00:09:40.165
You're a busy man

00:09:40.166 --> 00:09:46.083
Nothing like that, I have listened
to what you said I'm curious as well

00:09:46.208 --> 00:09:48.583
But what to do I'm tied up for a while now

00:09:48.750 --> 00:09:51.583
Actually if we get a solution
we might save his life

