He indulges in occasional intoxication
but isn't as meritless as his brother

00:17:52.791 --> 00:17:53.583
What about Sukumar?

00:17:53.708 --> 00:17:58.708
Sukumar? Sukumar is a very impressive chap,
a medical student in his 5th year.

00:17:59.791 --> 00:18:03.750
Sukumar returned late last night, isn't it?

00:18:29.000 --> 00:18:31.750
Here's the proof of my Bioscope visit.

00:18:32.708 --> 00:18:34.416
Give it to me.

00:18:35.000 --> 00:18:39.291
Karali babu didn't approve of
staying out till late at night.

00:18:40.208 --> 00:18:42.958
Despite that what is the reason
that you went for a night show?

00:18:43.208 --> 00:18:46.291
Reason..umm So you are the heir
to Karali Babu's entire property?

00:18:47.166 --> 00:18:50.666
Yes.
- That's a great deal of money, isnt it?

00:18:52.583 --> 00:18:55.333
When was the last time you met Karali Babu?

00:18:57.000 --> 00:19:01.208
Uncle, spare me from this burden of shame.

00:19:02.000 --> 00:19:03.708
That means you don't want my inheritance?

00:19:03.833 --> 00:19:05.500
It would be inaccurate if I say no

00:19:05.625 --> 00:19:06.707
But I don't want it all by myself

00:19:06.708 --> 00:19:11.000
Why don't you equally distribute
your property amongst all of us.

00:19:11.333 --> 00:19:15.500
I see, so this boy is trying to
be the flagbearer of equality..

00:19:16.416 --> 00:19:18.750
How dare you contradict me?

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:22.416
Uncle, I didn't mean to
disrespect your decision...

00:19:23.083 --> 00:19:25.290
But how can I deprive
everyone else from it...

00:19:25.291 --> 00:19:27.291
Out! Get out from here!!

00:19:27.583 --> 00:19:29.750
I am not going to give you a single penny!

00:19:30.166 --> 00:19:34.041
You rascal..belial..get
lost from here, get out!

00:19:46.291 --> 00:19:50.708
Are you suspecting Sukumar
to be the muderer?

00:19:51.666 --> 00:19:54.958
Sukumar? How's it possible?
You said Motilal is the murderer.

00:19:55.208 --> 00:19:57.000
Yes.
- So?

00:19:57.458 --> 00:20:00.208
This is Satyabati's room, right?
- Yes

00:20:00.958 --> 00:20:06.041
But why trouble a woman? I have
already taken her deposition.

00:20:06.375 --> 00:20:09.125
Oh, you've taken an account. Alright then.

00:20:09.416 --> 00:20:11.500
Still let's visit once.

00:20:23.541 --> 00:20:25.000
Listen, we want to...

00:20:28.750 --> 00:20:30.833
Don't mind us bothering you for a while.

00:20:31.666 --> 00:20:36.250
After this accident this police interrogation
must feel like rubbing salt on your wounds.

00:20:36.583 --> 00:20:41.291
Listen, unnecessarily don't defame
the Police, you're not one of us!

00:20:43.375 --> 00:20:45.500
I'm only going to ask a couple of questions

00:20:57.041 --> 00:21:00.750
For Karali Babu, every morning you
used to... Pardon me, may I sit?

00:21:01.000 --> 00:21:02.875
Hmm
- Thank you!

00:21:03.125 --> 00:21:05.875
You used to make tea and wake
Karali Babu up everyday, isnt it?

00:21:07.708 --> 00:21:10.916
Today was no different...
only that you found him dead

00:21:14.333 --> 00:21:18.666
You didn't know anything before that?
- What silly questions!

00:21:19.291 --> 00:21:22.041
Karali Babu's room's door
remained open all the time?

00:21:22.250 --> 00:21:25.583
No one was allowed to lock
their doors while sleeping.

00:21:26.500 --> 00:21:29.250
Uncle used to do the same.

00:21:32.041 --> 00:21:33.791
Then...

00:21:34.208 --> 00:21:37.083
Enough is enough, you don't
even know how to cross check!

00:21:37.250 --> 00:21:41.559
Listen Bidhu Babu, if you constantly interrupt me I'll
file a legal complaint against you to the commisioner.

00:21:41.583 --> 00:21:44.333
You don't want it, do you?

00:21:50.291 --> 00:21:53.041
You really didn't know anything
about it before, give it a thought!

00:21:55.208 --> 00:21:58.833
Given it a thought. I didn't know anything!

00:21:59.541 --> 00:22:02.291
Okay, how many spoons of sugar
Karali babu used to take?

00:22:03.708 --> 00:22:06.458
Sugar?
- Sugar.

00:22:07.333 --> 00:22:11.875
Uncle used to take quite an extra amount of sugar
with tea... around three to four tablespoons.

00:22:12.125 --> 00:22:14.583
My goodness, three to four tablespoons!

00:22:15.041 --> 00:22:16.841
So why didn't you add
sugar in his tea today?

00:22:21.708 --> 00:22:29.708
Actually... Actually... I am not feeling
well today... Maybe that is why...

00:22:34.333 --> 00:22:35.500
Where is the needle?

00:22:38.500 --> 00:22:39.874
Needle?

00:22:39.875 --> 00:22:42.041
Yes, needle. You use it for sewing right?

00:22:42.458 --> 00:22:45.208
And I can't find the thimble as well.

00:22:55.000 --> 00:22:57.750
It would have been beneficial for you all
if you could open up.

00:22:59.291 --> 00:23:00.291
I'll take a leave.

00:23:24.166 --> 00:23:28.583
You know what Bidhubabu, I'm yet to learn
the art of patience from you.

00:23:29.291 --> 00:23:31.457
Whatever it is, a senior like me..
- How's this Fanibhushan chap?

00:23:31.458 --> 00:23:33.041
Who?
- Fanibhushan.

00:23:33.208 --> 00:23:35.000
Fanibhushan is a cripple.

00:23:35.583 --> 00:23:38.666
And although the saying goes that 'a
crippled body hosts a crippled mind'...

00:23:39.375 --> 00:23:41.957
but if compared to the other
3 brothers he seems more humane.

00:23:41.958 --> 00:23:42.958
Humane?

00:23:43.458 --> 00:23:44.125
Let's find out.

00:23:44.126 --> 00:23:46.291
Where?
- To Fanibhushan's room.

00:23:53.166 --> 00:23:55.916
Nomoshkar (Greetings) sit, sit.
- Yes

00:23:57.666 --> 00:24:03.500
Byomkesh babu, my brother might be
short-tempered but he is not a murderer.

00:24:04.333 --> 00:24:06.500
I don't believe he has done this.

00:24:08.625 --> 00:24:12.875
You don't think even losing out on the inheritance
could make him do this out of aversion?

00:24:14.958 --> 00:24:19.415
In that case all three of us have that
excuse. Why only doubt Dada (elder brother)?

00:24:19.416 --> 00:24:21.375
Right, absolutely right.

00:24:21.833 --> 00:24:23.666
How's your equation with Karali Babu?

00:24:24.916 --> 00:24:32.583
I am a cripple, useless. Probably
that is why he sympathized with me.

00:24:33.125 --> 00:24:38.207
If Uncle didn't give me shelter,
maybe I would have starved to death.

00:24:38.208 --> 00:24:42.128
I guess you're aware that according to Karali Babu's
last will Sukumar is the heir to his property.

00:24:43.333 --> 00:24:47.583
Of course, Sukumar is the most
suitable one. - Most suitable one.

00:24:48.666 --> 00:24:51.791
In that case, have you decided
what you are going to do?

00:24:52.125 --> 00:24:55.416
If Sukumar permits, then I'll stay here.

00:24:55.625 --> 00:24:57.083
Or else...

00:24:57.375 --> 00:24:59.541
Fani, dada has been arrested.

00:25:00.958 --> 00:25:03.000
So you are Makhon?
- And you?

00:25:03.041 --> 00:25:05.457
Don't worry, I am not a policeman,
just a mere truthseeker (Satyanweshi).

00:25:05.458 --> 00:25:08.790
Satyanweshi Byomkesh Bakshi?
I don't know anything.

00:25:08.791 --> 00:25:10.957
Believe me I don't know anything.

00:25:10.958 --> 00:25:13.583
Believe me, sir I don't know anything.

00:25:14.541 --> 00:25:17.916
For god's sake, I don't know anything
Please let me go!

00:25:18.166 --> 00:25:21.791
Bastard. You're trying to fool Bidhu
Bhattacharya? Confess everything! Confess!

00:25:21.875 --> 00:25:26.958
Believe me, believe me Buddhu Babu.
- It's not Buddhu Babu, it's Bidhu Babu.

00:25:27.708 --> 00:25:32.000
Yes, yes. I am an alcoholic imbecile.
It's only wine and women that concerns me.

00:25:32.916 --> 00:25:38.333
I was with Dalim last night, she's
a witness. I don't know anything!

00:25:39.041 --> 00:25:43.541
From where is he arrested?
- A concubine's home, near Jorasanko.

00:25:44.041 --> 00:25:50.666
The entire city is under the surveillance of Bidhu
Bhattacharya. Not a single fly can escape it.

00:25:51.416 --> 00:25:53.583
Well, it's late you may go home now!

00:25:53.708 --> 00:25:57.500
Shall get him confessed after
a good thrash! Hey, get him.

00:25:57.833 --> 00:25:58.833
Come!

00:26:00.291 --> 00:26:02.458
Please leave me, I know nothing.

00:26:32.083 --> 00:26:34.250
What are you writing, Ajit?

00:26:35.708 --> 00:26:38.125
Anandabazar is publishing a
literary magazine called Desh

00:26:38.541 --> 00:26:41.125
And calling for new writers,
penning a piece for it.

00:26:42.458 --> 00:26:43.957
But what I have read in the morning

00:26:43.958 --> 00:26:46.125
It's difficult to render
something worthy after that.

00:26:46.541 --> 00:26:49.790
Had the French naturalist
Émile Zola read that

00:26:49.791 --> 00:26:51.231
He would have been equally disgusted

00:26:52.291 --> 00:26:53.707
What exactly did you read?

00:26:53.708 --> 00:26:56.166
Don't you remember whom did
I visit in the morning?

00:26:56.750 --> 00:27:00.166
Umm..morning..
Oh, that tarantula toxin.

00:27:01.125 --> 00:27:03.291
I almost forgot.

00:27:03.791 --> 00:27:07.000
Alright, so tell me what
did you see in that house?

00:27:08.916 --> 00:27:11.875
Listen then, I reached that house...

00:27:29.458 --> 00:27:31.625
Whom have you brought, doctor?

00:27:31.916 --> 00:27:34.083
Tell him to leave.

00:27:43.916 --> 00:27:45.290
Again you've taken it today?

00:27:45.291 --> 00:27:47.875
It's my choice. It's nobody's business!

00:27:49.083 --> 00:27:51.250
God knows from where
he's getting the poison

00:27:51.500 --> 00:27:54.916
Neither could we figure when he's taking it

00:27:57.416 --> 00:28:01.040
Listen, this poison is
affecting your health

00:28:01.041 --> 00:28:03.207
It's damaging your brain.

00:28:03.208 --> 00:28:06.750
But your brain works absolutely fine,

00:28:07.208 --> 00:28:09.875
Why can't you find out?

00:28:10.375 --> 00:28:12.833
Also kept my house under surveillance.

00:28:13.500 --> 00:28:15.666
Even they are unable to find it out.

00:28:15.958 --> 00:28:21.457
Nincompoops! Can't find out... Hahaha!

00:28:21.458 --> 00:28:22.499
Nomoshkar, Nandadulal Babu!

00:28:22.500 --> 00:28:24.666
Shut up! There is no need for all these.

00:28:28.333 --> 00:28:34.082
Beside you both there is no one
who goes into his room, isn't it?

00:28:34.083 --> 00:28:35.083
No

00:28:37.125 --> 00:28:38.583
Does he receive any letters?

00:28:38.791 --> 00:28:42.125
Yes, once a week there is a
registry mail, from Kolkata.

00:28:42.333 --> 00:28:45.166
A lady named Rebecca Lite sends them.

00:28:47.750 --> 00:28:52.791
Only blank papers and nothing else.

00:28:56.875 --> 00:29:00.750
Does your father, Nandadulal
Babu, write to anyone?

00:29:01.125 --> 00:29:02.125
No.

00:29:03.041 --> 00:29:10.041
But he sends a money order of 100 rupees
to Rebecca Lite every month.

00:29:14.125 --> 00:29:17.541
How does the thing enter his house...

00:29:18.916 --> 00:29:22.541
And how does Nandadulal babu take it...

00:29:23.625 --> 00:29:28.000
What is the purpose of the
blank registered paper?

00:29:28.500 --> 00:29:32.083
And what is the reason
behind sending her money?

00:29:33.416 --> 00:29:35.583
Give it a thought, Ajit.

00:29:37.791 --> 00:29:41.250
I have thought about all these, a lot of
times. Nothing is getting in my head.

00:29:42.208 --> 00:29:46.041
Let's hear about your current case!

00:29:46.375 --> 00:29:49.166
Do you think Motilal is the culprit?

00:29:53.875 --> 00:29:55.333
Then who?

00:29:57.041 --> 00:29:58.875
Who?

00:30:08.875 --> 00:30:13.500
Keeping Motilal aside, there remains
Fani, Makhon, Sukumar and Satyabati...

00:30:13.916 --> 00:30:16.083
Everyone has equal motives.

00:30:16.750 --> 00:30:18.875
Satyabati too?
- Why not?

00:30:18.916 --> 00:30:20.250
But what can be her motive?

00:30:20.583 --> 00:30:23.059
According to Karali's last will her brother
is the sole proprietor of his assets.

00:30:23.083 --> 00:30:25.374
The one who changes his
will so frequently...

00:30:25.375 --> 00:30:28.375
If he's murdered there won't be
any such further possibilities

00:30:30.583 --> 00:30:35.833
Hence, Satyabati too can't be
waived off the suspect list, Ajit.

00:30:39.791 --> 00:30:41.708
So Byomkesh

00:30:41.833 --> 00:30:46.458
You're suggesting that it
is chloroform marks in Karali Babu's nose?

00:30:49.875 --> 00:30:52.166
Can't disclose this to Buddhu Babu

00:30:53.625 --> 00:30:55.916
He thinks it is phlegm mark.

00:30:58.208 --> 00:31:00.875
The murder took place at 12am...

00:31:01.000 --> 00:31:03.291
How can you say it so convincingly?

00:31:06.083 --> 00:31:08.375
Conjecture...

00:31:08.791 --> 00:31:11.083
But what I can't decipher is...

00:31:12.666 --> 00:31:18.666
Why did the murderer
kept the needle pierced?

00:31:19.208 --> 00:31:22.833
Had he taken it out there
would have been no evidence!

00:31:23.291 --> 00:31:29.250
Few significant portions is marked in red
from Grey's Anatomy in Sukumar's room

00:31:29.291 --> 00:31:31.583
But where is that pencil?

00:31:35.166 --> 00:31:37.458
What was written in those
marked portions from the book?

00:31:40.125 --> 00:31:44.040
If a needle is pierced right at the
junction of Medulla and First Vertebrae...

00:31:44.041 --> 00:31:45.958
it'll cause instant death.

00:31:55.416 --> 00:31:58.416
The cook and the servant are
the sole witness to the will

00:31:58.541 --> 00:32:02.291
Yes, these two. Give.

00:32:05.000 --> 00:32:09.166
Bidhubabu, we could have looked
for the rest of the rooms..

00:32:09.500 --> 00:32:13.208
What's the need? I have done
it all and found the culprit

00:32:13.375 --> 00:32:16.333
Why get involved in all
these unnecessarily?

00:32:16.458 --> 00:32:18.583
Makes sense!
- Hmm

00:32:21.708 --> 00:32:24.666
I'll leave then.
- Where?

00:32:25.375 --> 00:32:27.041
I'll go home only...

00:32:27.208 --> 00:32:30.916
but before that if I could drop by the
commissioner's office once...

00:32:31.208 --> 00:32:32.750
Needed to report to him.

00:32:32.833 --> 00:32:33.957
So Byomkesh Babu
- Yes, tell me?

00:32:33.958 --> 00:32:36.708
I was saying which rooms
needed to be searched?

00:32:39.125 --> 00:32:40.125
Come, I'll tell you.

00:32:56.541 --> 00:33:00.916
With reference to, today,
22nd September 1933

00:33:00.958 --> 00:33:05.458
I declare this will being
in sound senses...

00:33:06.000 --> 00:33:09.374
after my demise all my tangible
and intangible assests...

00:33:09.375 --> 00:33:11.083
and other relevant properties...

00:33:11.166 --> 00:33:15.125
will be inherited by my youngest
niece Shri Fanibhushan...

00:33:16.250 --> 00:33:20.791
Hence, from today, all my
previous will becomes invalid.

00:33:20.916 --> 00:33:24.083
Undersigned, Shri Karalicharan Basu.

00:33:25.375 --> 00:33:30.333
Oh boy! You wanted to obliterate
this will, didn't you?

00:33:30.708 --> 00:33:33.666
Sir, this bottle of chloroform
has been found as well.

00:33:33.833 --> 00:33:35.791
What?
- Yes, sir

00:33:35.958 --> 00:33:38.832
The marks which were there
in Karali Babu's nose...

00:33:38.833 --> 00:33:40.624
those were chloroform marks.

00:33:40.625 --> 00:33:44.333
Byomkesh Babu was saying this.
- Shut up!

00:33:44.375 --> 00:33:47.541
Byomkesh babu were saying?
He's a young chap. What does he know?

00:33:47.583 --> 00:33:50.125
I said it, what?
- Yes, yes.

00:33:51.125 --> 00:33:52.375
Here take it!

00:33:53.458 --> 00:33:58.625
What does that metal cap called
which protects the finger while sewing?

00:33:58.791 --> 00:34:00.458
Thimble?

00:34:00.666 --> 00:34:03.375
Thimble, thimble. Has it been found?

00:34:03.583 --> 00:34:05.875
No sir, that has is not found.

00:34:06.041 --> 00:34:07.333
Not found?
- No sir.

00:34:07.458 --> 00:34:10.708
Who knows how much till
will it take to find it.

00:34:10.833 --> 00:34:13.875
Anyway, go and put him behind the bars.

00:34:14.000 --> 00:34:15.416
Sir.

00:34:15.791 --> 00:34:17.291
Bring him.

00:34:18.291 --> 00:34:20.458
You've set Motilal free finally?

00:34:21.083 --> 00:34:24.250
Bidhubabu has gotten into senses.

00:34:24.458 --> 00:34:28.166
Apart from Sukumar's had anyone else's
room been searched?

00:34:30.708 --> 00:34:32.375
No. Why?

00:34:34.750 --> 00:34:37.375
To Bidhubabu nothing seems necessary.

00:34:38.250 --> 00:34:43.625
Inspite of having overwhelming evidences
against Sukumar, the investigation must go on.

00:34:44.458 --> 00:34:48.708
Until that red pencil and
the thimble are found...

00:34:49.500 --> 00:34:51.583
It isn't advisable to
cease the investigation

00:34:52.041 --> 00:34:53.708
Have you got the medical reports?

00:34:56.500 --> 00:34:58.333
What is the time of death?

00:35:00.166 --> 00:35:03.875
3 hours after dinner which
means around 12, isnt it?

00:35:05.458 --> 00:35:09.166
Alright, thank you. I'll be there tomorrow.

00:35:14.333 --> 00:35:17.458
Byomkesh, that means
Sukumar is the murderer.

00:35:19.333 --> 00:35:20.833
See, Ajit...

00:35:22.125 --> 00:35:25.290
It seems like someone is
trying to make it obvious...

00:35:25.291 --> 00:35:29.000
That Karali Babu has
been murdered by a doctor..

00:35:29.541 --> 00:35:33.250
This kind of murder is impossible
without the knowledge of anatomy.

00:35:34.625 --> 00:35:38.540
The needle which was used was stolen from
his sister's sewing box

00:35:38.541 --> 00:35:40.416
In fact the thread is exactly the same.

00:35:41.250 --> 00:35:43.166
And Sukumar confessed that..

00:35:43.208 --> 00:35:46.916
That he had a tiff with
Karali babu that night.

00:35:48.416 --> 00:35:52.916
For him it was apparent that Karali Babu
would have changed his will again

00:35:54.541 --> 00:35:57.416
The motive behind the murder is clear.

00:35:57.958 --> 00:35:59.583
Then where is the doubt?

00:35:59.833 --> 00:36:03.541
Everything is being laid out in front
of our eyes very clearly, Ajit...

00:36:05.500 --> 00:36:07.375
That is where the doubt remains.

00:36:16.750 --> 00:36:21.041
Byomkesh babu, please save my brother...

00:36:26.041 --> 00:36:27.500
My brother is innocent...

00:36:29.000 --> 00:36:30.708
He doesn't know anything...

00:36:31.208 --> 00:36:32.541
without offence...

00:36:32.583 --> 00:36:34.458
But all evidences are against him...

00:36:35.000 --> 00:36:36.541
All lies...

00:36:37.583 --> 00:36:40.750
He can't murder anyone for property...

00:36:41.000 --> 00:36:43.958
We don't need any property,
Byomkesh Babu...

00:36:44.208 --> 00:36:47.208
Please save my brother from this trouble...

00:36:48.208 --> 00:36:51.291
My brother didn't commit
any crime, trust me!

00:36:51.625 --> 00:36:54.583
I need to know everything
before I trust you.

00:36:54.791 --> 00:36:56.875
But I haven't hidden anything.

00:36:57.125 --> 00:36:58.916
You have, you have
undoubtedly hidden facts.

00:36:59.458 --> 00:37:03.166
That very night you got to know about
Karali babu's death but didn't tell me.

00:37:06.833 --> 00:37:07.953
Are you going to say it now?

00:37:16.666 --> 00:37:19.083
When I went to Uncle's room...

00:37:19.166 --> 00:37:20.999
There was a smell...

00:37:21.000 --> 00:37:23.166
not very strong rather a sweet one...

00:37:23.625 --> 00:37:25.250
Can't really define the smell.

00:37:25.291 --> 00:37:26.291
Hmm.. chloroform

00:37:48.625 --> 00:37:49.625
After that?

00:37:50.541 --> 00:37:54.250
The next morning some how
I made tea and went to Uncle's room...

00:38:06.833 --> 00:38:10.541
Oh traveler have you lost your way?

00:38:12.875 --> 00:38:15.000
What exactly happened?

00:38:15.333 --> 00:38:19.875
I mean did the sleuth
just become solicitous?

00:38:20.833 --> 00:38:23.333
Insinuating me, Ajit?

00:38:24.500 --> 00:38:26.250
Looking for a path only.

