Byomkesh, I really enjoyed the bioscope.

00:39:17.291 --> 00:39:20.250
Listen Ajit, what solution did you
find abot the Tarantula case?

00:39:20.375 --> 00:39:25.750
Oh, I think I have found a solution.

00:39:26.000 --> 00:39:27.958
Oh really? Tell me then...

00:39:28.250 --> 00:39:33.416
Inside Nandadulal babu's room, in corners,
right to left I have noticed spiders...

00:39:33.500 --> 00:39:35.666
When there is no one at
home, in that room...

