But why?
- I'll worship it every morning

00:40:14.583 --> 00:40:18.291
Why are you laughing like a lunatic?

00:40:28.125 --> 00:40:30.583
Ajit, is the color of
Nandadulal babu's tongue red?

00:40:32.250 --> 00:40:33.250
Why?

00:40:33.833 --> 00:40:35.333
Find out.

00:40:39.833 --> 00:40:42.333
There lies the actual
solution of this mystery.

00:40:50.916 --> 00:40:55.583
Byomkesh babu, this Sukumar
is the real culprit...

00:40:55.750 --> 00:40:57.415
I knew this from the very beginning

00:40:57.416 --> 00:40:59.416
Really?
- Yes, didn't let anyone understand!

00:40:59.500 --> 00:41:02.375
Was toying with him a bit.
- Impressive!

00:41:04.458 --> 00:41:08.000
What?
- Was looking for your toying equipment!

00:41:14.708 --> 00:41:15.708
Ajit.

00:41:16.916 --> 00:41:18.875
Bidhubabu, look what a strange thing!

00:41:19.875 --> 00:41:21.583
Hush!!

00:41:26.000 --> 00:41:29.541
Bidhubabu, keep him in your custody
for a while. Ajit come with me.

00:41:29.625 --> 00:41:30.125
Wait.

00:41:30.541 --> 00:41:34.083
Bidhubabu, till then keep
this man toying for a while.

00:41:36.000 --> 00:41:39.541
Uncle lost his life only for some money!

00:41:40.291 --> 00:41:43.375
As the saying goes, money
is the root of all evil.

00:41:45.833 --> 00:41:49.374
No, Byomkesh Babu this heirship
doesn't make me happy.

00:41:49.375 --> 00:41:51.250
This one is a physiology book.

00:41:53.000 --> 00:41:54.208
Must be Sukumar Babu's.

00:41:54.500 --> 00:41:59.625
Sometimes Sukumar used to lend
me his physiology books to read.

00:42:01.250 --> 00:42:04.375
I used to consider him the
closest in this house.

00:42:05.125 --> 00:42:07.499
But who knows what goes
inside one's mind...

00:42:07.500 --> 00:42:09.375
It's difficult to discern that.

00:42:14.833 --> 00:42:17.416
Fanibabu, you seem to
be a diligent bookworm.

00:42:19.166 --> 00:42:21.541
Yes, that is how I'm sustaining

00:42:22.833 --> 00:42:25.207
So Byomkesh Babu...

00:42:25.208 --> 00:42:30.208
do you really think Sukumar
is the one to be blamed?

00:42:31.375 --> 00:42:37.583
The evidences are redirecting the
clouds of doubt towards him.

00:42:38.791 --> 00:42:40.666
Do I explain it to you?

00:42:42.500 --> 00:42:44.958
One thing is clear from this...

00:42:45.583 --> 00:42:46.583
The culprit...

00:42:47.666 --> 00:42:50.083
is naive and clever at the same time...

00:42:51.375 --> 00:42:53.335
He executed the murder in
an extremely clever way

00:42:54.250 --> 00:42:59.291
But he had kept all the evidences
in his room like a fool.

00:43:01.000 --> 00:43:03.708
As if Sukumar had to use Satyabati's
needle for the murder...

00:43:05.541 --> 00:43:08.083
and hide the will in his room...

00:43:08.625 --> 00:43:10.166
He could have just tore it off...

00:43:10.291 --> 00:43:12.833
What do you understand from this?
- What?

00:43:14.666 --> 00:43:15.833
You understand this that...

00:43:15.875 --> 00:43:18.375
the criminal is not a fool
but a very clever one...

00:43:18.416 --> 00:43:19.666
and intelligent...

00:43:20.666 --> 00:43:23.625
But Fanibabu, even a watchful man
can flounder, like in this case...

00:43:25.625 --> 00:43:26.625
What?

00:43:27.208 --> 00:43:28.083
Let me explain...

00:43:28.208 --> 00:43:29.250
What mistake?

00:43:29.666 --> 00:43:30.666
But before that...

00:43:32.083 --> 00:43:34.003
give me a pencil I'd like
to make a blueprint...

00:43:34.250 --> 00:43:36.130
Ajit, kindly see if you
get a paper anywhere...

00:43:36.625 --> 00:43:38.540
Yes, give me a pencil.
- Here you go.

00:43:38.541 --> 00:43:39.749
Yes, give it to me.

00:43:39.750 --> 00:43:42.875
Got anything?
Let it be, you may sit.

00:43:43.208 --> 00:43:45.489
Okay, a blueprint isn't required
anymore, let me say it...

00:43:46.208 --> 00:43:50.083
In this case the culprit
made three mistakes...

00:43:50.625 --> 00:43:51.625
Firstly...

00:43:52.083 --> 00:43:54.750
In the Grey's Anatomy book...

00:43:55.375 --> 00:43:58.875
he had marked a particular
portion with a red pencil...

00:43:59.916 --> 00:44:03.041
Secondly, he doesn't know about
the jurisdiction in good order...

00:44:04.375 --> 00:44:05.874
Doesn't know about legalities properly?

00:44:05.875 --> 00:44:07.040
No, doesn't know properly at all...

00:44:07.041 --> 00:44:08.624
Hence the crime he
committed went in vain...

00:44:08.625 --> 00:44:10.500
absolutely futile... Fanibabu.

00:44:10.791 --> 00:44:11.791
What?

00:44:11.875 --> 00:44:13.957
Ajit..Ajit..Ajit...

00:44:13.958 --> 00:44:15.208
What do you mean to suggest?

00:44:15.875 --> 00:44:17.582
Take a look at this will...

00:44:17.583 --> 00:44:19.708
This was discovered from
Sukuma Babu's room...

00:44:19.833 --> 00:44:22.790
The will is invalid legally,
it doesn't have a signature of a witness..

00:44:22.791 --> 00:44:24.726
No authorized witness signatory?
What are you saying?

00:44:24.750 --> 00:44:26.207
Wait I'll make it clearer...

00:44:26.208 --> 00:44:28.083
No, no, no wait..
- Let me explain, just listen

00:44:28.416 --> 00:44:29.416
Listen carefully...

00:44:29.750 --> 00:44:33.125
You had instructed Makhon to get the
bottel of chloroform beforehand...

00:44:34.041 --> 00:44:37.083
That evening when Sukumar had
a fight with Karali Babu...

00:44:37.291 --> 00:44:39.166
You had a doubt...

00:44:39.250 --> 00:44:42.041
That Karali Babu might
change his will again...

00:44:42.208 --> 00:44:44.083
And this time it was going be your turn...

00:44:44.583 --> 00:44:46.041
And it was as you expected...

00:44:46.458 --> 00:44:49.874
But you wanted to ensure Karali Babu
doesn't get to change his will...

00:44:49.875 --> 00:44:52.708
So it was necessary to remove him
from being an obstacle..

00:44:53.500 --> 00:44:55.875
But due to your lack of prowess...

00:44:56.291 --> 00:44:59.833
you had to pierce the needle thrice
to hit the exact place.

00:45:00.125 --> 00:45:03.541
A medical student like Sukumar
would have done it at one go.

00:45:05.083 --> 00:45:06.707
If you would have kept the
will at its right place...

00:45:06.708 --> 00:45:08.916
you couldn't have framed Sukumar...

00:45:09.291 --> 00:45:12.416
At the same time you must frame
another to save yourself...

00:45:13.000 --> 00:45:16.458
So you hid the will and the bottle
of chloroform in Sukumar's room...

00:45:16.708 --> 00:45:20.000
You were aware that each room will be
ransacked after this incident...

00:45:21.250 --> 00:45:22.958
Then the Will would be found too...

00:45:24.041 --> 00:45:25.921
You planned to kill two
birds with one stone...

00:45:26.916 --> 00:45:30.142
Firstly, Sukumar would be hanged and on the
other hand you would inherit the property...

00:45:30.166 --> 00:45:31.166
Isn't it so?

00:45:35.208 --> 00:45:36.625
Have you thrown the thimble away?

00:45:38.250 --> 00:45:40.041
Give me some time Byomkesh Babu...

00:45:41.458 --> 00:45:43.625
I'm not feeling very well...

00:45:44.833 --> 00:45:45.958
Get ready.

00:45:49.958 --> 00:45:52.750
(weeping) - You're not paying
attention, I'm asking you something...

00:45:52.875 --> 00:45:53.208
What is he saying?

00:45:53.209 --> 00:45:54.874
Who asked you to get the chloroform?

00:45:54.875 --> 00:45:56.582
Tell me now!

00:45:56.583 --> 00:45:57.666
Fani asked me to...

00:45:58.250 --> 00:45:58.708
Fani?

00:45:58.750 --> 00:46:01.624
He couldn't sleep at night,
one drop of chloroform would help so...

00:46:01.625 --> 00:46:03.500
You think this is some kind of joke?

00:46:03.583 --> 00:46:04.642
Chloroform is no sleeping pill...

00:46:04.666 --> 00:46:05.750
Bidhubabu, let him go..

00:46:09.458 --> 00:46:10.458
Byomkesh Babu...

00:46:10.791 --> 00:46:12.791
What exactly do you mean to suggest?

00:46:12.875 --> 00:46:14.392
Once you're saying to take him in custody,
again you're saying to let him go...

00:46:14.416 --> 00:46:17.177
Never meant to take him in custody,
just asked you to play with him...

00:46:18.750 --> 00:46:19.874
What is the matter...

00:46:19.875 --> 00:46:20.791
Listen Byomkesh Babu...

00:46:20.792 --> 00:46:23.749
Just because you are in good
terms with the commissioner...

00:46:23.750 --> 00:46:25.208
You can't always...

00:46:25.541 --> 00:46:28.875
Mock and joke with me and get by...

00:46:28.958 --> 00:46:32.083
Tell me honestly,
who is the actual murderer of Karali Babu?

00:48:07.916 --> 00:48:10.416
Byomkesh Babu, I'll take your leave then...

00:48:10.583 --> 00:48:12.250
I'm an useless cripple...

00:48:12.791 --> 00:48:14.749
No one will help me sustain here...

00:48:14.750 --> 00:48:18.166
I didn't get the money, hence
find no reason to be alive...

00:48:19.458 --> 00:48:21.166
Uncle didn't love me...

00:48:22.708 --> 00:48:24.583
Instead ridiculed me for being a cripple...

00:48:25.375 --> 00:48:28.500
Therefore I have no guilt
for murdering him...

00:48:28.916 --> 00:48:31.208
But I feel apologetic to Sukumar...

00:48:31.541 --> 00:48:35.000
Apart from him, I couldn't
have framed another...

00:48:35.916 --> 00:48:37.541
Also, if Sukumar was hanged...

00:48:37.750 --> 00:48:40.125
It would have been beneficial
for me in another way...

00:48:40.333 --> 00:48:43.207
But the embarrassment of being a cripple...

00:48:43.208 --> 00:48:46.041
restrained me from
expressing it to anyone.

00:48:46.875 --> 00:48:49.500
I'll not express it today as well...

00:48:50.458 --> 00:48:54.375
I had stolen the thimble and the
needle from Satyabati's room...

00:48:55.750 --> 00:48:58.875
No one could have gotten
me caught except you...

00:49:00.291 --> 00:49:04.375
But I still couldn't detest you...

00:49:06.458 --> 00:49:07.541
Farewell.

00:49:20.291 --> 00:49:21.291
So Byomkesh...

00:49:23.625 --> 00:49:26.958
Where do you go everyday all decked up,
that too at the same time...

00:49:27.541 --> 00:49:29.208
Any new case?

00:49:29.958 --> 00:49:31.833
Hmm but a rather secret one...

00:49:32.333 --> 00:49:34.708
Your new client seems epicurean...

00:49:34.791 --> 00:49:37.374
Chosen a detective wearing Nehru
Coat (Waist coat), Panjabi...

00:49:37.375 --> 00:49:39.958
Oops! Truth seeker...

00:49:40.166 --> 00:49:42.250
Seeking the truth isn't
an easy task, Ajit...

00:49:42.583 --> 00:49:44.333
You need to be well prepared for that.

00:49:45.250 --> 00:49:47.750
Well, you have been seeking the
truth for quite a while...

00:49:48.041 --> 00:49:50.624
Never seen you in this attire...

00:49:50.625 --> 00:49:52.185
It's a different kind of truth, Ajit...

00:49:52.375 --> 00:49:54.142
A bachelor like you won't
be able to figure it out.

00:49:54.166 --> 00:49:55.833
You're right actually...

00:49:56.375 --> 00:49:59.333
Hey! But you didn't give me a
solution for the Tarantula mystery...

00:50:00.291 --> 00:50:02.124
Did you find out the color
of Nandadula Babu's tongue?

00:50:02.125 --> 00:50:03.083
Red.

00:50:03.084 --> 00:50:05.041
That is it, it is solved.

00:50:05.083 --> 00:50:06.125
What is solved?

00:50:07.250 --> 00:50:10.375
Ajit, you still couldn't understand?

00:50:11.041 --> 00:50:11.750
Okay, listen...

00:50:11.791 --> 00:50:13.332
You ask Mohan Babu or Arun Babu...

00:50:13.333 --> 00:50:18.750
To get rid of the red ink pot and the fountain
pen from his room, that will be enough.

00:50:41.750 --> 00:50:45.166
The red ink pot contains
the Tarantula toxin...

00:50:46.791 --> 00:50:48.750
But who is getting it from outside?

00:50:48.916 --> 00:50:50.625
Think harder, you'll understand.

00:51:14.625 --> 00:51:15.833
The peon?

00:51:19.125 --> 00:51:20.624
And why the money order?

00:51:20.625 --> 00:51:22.458
Oh Ajit, use your brain...

00:51:25.125 --> 00:51:27.333
To pay for the substance.

00:51:28.083 --> 00:51:29.707
That's like it, you've
understood everything...

00:51:29.708 --> 00:51:32.000
Listen Ajit, let me tell
you something important...

00:51:32.041 --> 00:51:33.125
For the next few days...

00:51:33.166 --> 00:51:35.999
I'll be extremely busy regarding
a very important case...

00:51:36.000 --> 00:51:37.582
To seek a truth...

00:51:37.583 --> 00:51:39.457
In the meantime if any new case arises...

00:51:39.458 --> 00:51:41.250
I'd expect you to resolve it yourself...

00:51:41.291 --> 00:51:41.916
Goodbye then.

00:51:41.917 --> 00:51:43.208
What do you mean?

00:51:44.958 --> 00:51:46.517
The meaning is really profound, Mr.
Banerjee...

00:51:46.541 --> 00:51:47.541
Bye.

00:51:59.208 --> 00:52:00.250
Do you...

00:52:02.333 --> 00:52:04.416
Do you like mystery?

00:52:04.750 --> 00:52:05.750
What?

00:52:05.958 --> 00:52:07.833
If you have to spend the
rest of your life...

00:52:08.291 --> 00:52:11.500
amidst murderers, frauds and imposters...

00:52:11.625 --> 00:52:13.040
on account of your partner...

00:52:13.041 --> 00:52:15.583
how inconvenient that would be for you?

00:52:16.208 --> 00:52:19.333
I am not getting what you are saying...

00:52:20.958 --> 00:52:23.125
In these crucial moments I
can't remember a poem...

00:52:24.791 --> 00:52:28.000
Oh yes, have you heard this poem...

00:52:29.666 --> 00:52:32.416
An ever floating wind impeded the path...

00:52:32.500 --> 00:52:34.375
No No No..wait a minute...

00:52:35.875 --> 00:52:36.875
Yes...

00:52:37.458 --> 00:52:40.041
Unrestrained affiliations
impeded the path...

00:52:41.041 --> 00:52:42.916
We are travellers of the buoyant breeze...

00:52:43.750 --> 00:52:46.625
But why are you mentioning The
Last Poem all of a sudden?

00:52:47.500 --> 00:52:49.250
Umm..why The Last Poem?

00:52:55.541 --> 00:52:56.625
For a beginning...

00:52:59.666 --> 00:53:03.416
I mean to say... can I umm to you...

00:53:06.166 --> 00:53:08.083
Umm as in?

00:53:09.375 --> 00:53:11.208
Umm as in marriage...

00:53:14.666 --> 00:53:17.958
Do you wish to marry me?

00:53:22.416 --> 00:53:24.791
You're getting what I mean to say, right?